---
source: tests/cli_help.rs
expression: stdout
---
Manage articles

Usage: mf article [OPTIONS] [COMMAND]

Commands:
  new      Create an article
  list     List articles [aliases: ls]
  lint     Lint articles
  index    Index articles
  rename   Rename an article
  remove   Remove an article [aliases: rm]
  show     Show article details
  update   Update article metadata
  convert  Convert article shape between directory and single-file

Options:
      --root <PATH>      Mind Repo root directory
      --config <PATH>    Config file path
  -v, --verbose...       Verbose output
  -q, --quiet            Silence non-error output
      --format <FORMAT>  Output format [default: text] [possible values: text, json]
      --json             Shorthand for --format json
      --no-color         Disable colored output
  -p, --project <NAME>   Project name for project-scoped operations
  -h, --help             Print help
  -V, --version          Print version
